------
NOTES:
------

  -> SPI BAT: 8 Functional and 6 Performance (KPIs) TCs.

  -> 'spi-bat-tests' contains 6 functional TC

  -> 'spi-full-tests' contains functional, performance and stress TC.

  -> All TC are detailed in SPI Test Plan: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/12hmqWMBzK2IewCvdCpJOdB4QNbSpZoU_WYxpnuvQM8g/edit#gid=303960539

  -> To run SPI tests: './run_lck_test.sh -d spi -t <test-type> -k <kernel-type>'
    		         <test-type>:   bat, func, perf or full
			 <kernel-type>: module or builtin
